SUMMARY:Good Friday Event at United Methodist Church
DESCRIPTION:The United Methodist Churches of Lancaster City invite YOU to our Good Friday Event. On Friday April 3rd at Christ UMC 935 E Walnut St (parking behind church on Madison St.). Starting at 2:00 with the Stations of the Cross there will be reflective readings at each station and a hands-on object or activity to center you on Jesus’ journey to the cross. At 3:00 there will be a worship service with emphasis on Jesus’ Last Words. During worship there will be separate Children’s Time with activities.  Join us as we journey to Resurrection Sunday. The event will be rain or shine.
URL:https://figlancaster.com/event/good-friday-event-at-united-methodist-church/
LOCATION:Christ United Methodist Church\, 935 E Walnut St Parking behind church on Madison St\, LANCASTER\, PA\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Community
ORGANIZER;CN="United Methodist Churches of Lancaster City":MAILTO:rkimmich@aol.com
END:VEVENT
