SUMMARY:Lancaster Improv Players
DESCRIPTION:Spend your First Friday with your favorite fools this April! Join the Lancaster Improv Players as they play games popularized by Whose Line Is It Anyway and perform scenes based on your suggestions. If you like to laugh\, then you’re going to love this! Don’t miss the nonprofit troupe that has been making Lancaster a funnier place since 2015. \n            \n        \n                \n                \n    Learn More
