SUMMARY:Savage Cabaret: Electric Parlor Burlesque & Variety Show
DESCRIPTION:For two nights only\, burlesque\, drag and comedy take over City Hall at West Art\, where stained glass windows and soaring wooden beams set the stage for an unforgettable evening of glamour\, expression and mischief.\n\nThis special edition of Savage Cabaret brings the magic closer than ever before. With only 45 small tables per show\, audiences will experience vaudeville the way it was meant to be seen — intimate\, up close and personal.\n\nEach one-hour performance features a dazzling lineup of consisting of 3 burlesque artists\, one drag queen and one songstress\, creating a fast-paced\, high-energy cabaret experience that is as playful as it is intense.\n\nWhether you’re planning a girls’ night out\, a memorable date\, or simply looking for something extraordinary to do in Lancaster\, Savage Cabaret: Electric Parlor offers a night unlike anything else in Central Pennsylvania.\n\nTables seat two guests with the option to add a third chair.\n\nOnly 40 tables are available per show. Once they’re gone\, they’re gone.\n\nReserve yours now and get ready to feel the buzz! \n\n\n\n\n\n\n    Buy Tickets
URL:https://figlancaster.com/event/savage-cabaret-electric-parlor-burlesque-variety-show/2026-04-03/
LOCATION:West Art\, 800 Buchanan Ave\, Lancaster PA\, Lancaster\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts & Entertainment
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://fig.guide/content/uploads/sites/3/2026/03/Jhed_WestArt_P1.avif
ORGANIZER;CN="Bonafide Ivy":MAILTO:BonafideIvy@GMAIL.com
END:VEVENT
