SUMMARY:Adult Beginner Salsa
DESCRIPTION:It’s never too late to break in those dancing shoes! Learn the basic steps of salsa dancing in this engaging\, high-energy class designed for adult beginners. ¡Vámonos!\n\nWhat to wear:\n\n• Comfortable\, breathable clothing that allows for movement (e.g. leggings\, athletic wear\, t-shirts)\n• Jazz shoes\, dance shoes\, or clean sneakers\n• Hair pulled back if long\n• Water bottle encouraged for hydration \n            \n        \n                \n            \n                \n                \n    Register Now
