SUMMARY:Bowl For Kids Sake
DESCRIPTION:Bowl for Kids’ Sake is a fun and easy way for you and your company\, friends\, or family to support the life-changing work of Big Brothers Big Sisters of South-Central PA. If you believe in the power of mentorship and can spare a few hours to have fun\, then Bowl for Kids’ Sake is for you! Register today!\nWe request a team of 5 fundraise a minimum of $500 ($100 per person) \n            \n        \n                \n                \n    Register Now
