SUMMARY:Spring Open House at Thaddeus Stevens College
DESCRIPTION:One event: endless opportunities. Attend our Spring Open House! We’re looking forward to meeting future Bulldogs at our Open House on Saturday\, April 11th\, from 9 a.m. to 1 p.m.!\n\nOpen House offers a unique and engaging in-person opportunity to explore all that Thaddeus Stevens College of Technology has to offer. While visiting us for the Spring Open House\, plan to:\n– Spend time in your future program of study\, tour our labs\, and talk with faculty.\n– Connect with various support offices.\n– Speak with industry partners regarding the opportunities that await after earning a degree from Thaddeus Stevens College. \n            \n        \n                \n                \n    Register Now
